00:00:02.370 --> 00:00:05.650
WENDY LI: I have an interesting
relationship with photography.

00:00:05.650 --> 00:00:07.770
I came to this point
last year where

00:00:07.770 --> 00:00:11.770
I didn't know if I wanted to
even make photographs anymore.

00:00:11.770 --> 00:00:14.660
And I didn't know what I
wanted to take photographs of.

00:00:14.660 --> 00:00:17.740
I went back to sort
of asking myself--

00:00:17.740 --> 00:00:19.820
why do I love photography?


00:00:19.820 --> 00:00:21.900
And what about photography
makes it so interesting

00:00:21.900 --> 00:00:24.240
and makes it worth my time?


00:00:24.240 --> 00:00:25.620
My name is Wendy Li.


00:00:25.620 --> 00:00:27.940
I'm in the class of 2015.


00:00:27.940 --> 00:00:30.770
And I'm concentrating in
the Woodrow Wilson School

00:00:30.770 --> 00:00:32.460
with a certificate
in visual arts.

