are photos that

00:03:12.500 --> 00:03:14.300
could be in history textbooks.


00:03:14.300 --> 00:03:16.140
They're very removed,
especially for,

00:03:16.140 --> 00:03:19.790
I think, the average American
student at Princeton.

00:03:19.790 --> 00:03:22.520
They would look at
these and not be

00:03:22.520 --> 00:03:26.010
able to relate to them
personally at all.

00:03:26.010 --> 00:03:29.160
But I think when people start
moving through the timeline,

00:03:29.160 --> 00:03:31.410
