and as the photographs become

00:03:34.420 --> 00:03:37.560
more approachable
and more familiar,

00:03:37.560 --> 00:03:42.930
that they'll realize that these
seemingly alien concepts are

00:03:42.930 --> 00:03:48.100
actually real experiences
that you can relate to.

